data.title: Rap Pack
data.text:
The House of Checklists is provided as an information resource for

non-sports card collectors. The lists are not an offer to sell or

to buy. Please click on the image above to visit the main page.

Rap Pack Premier Cards - 1991

Note: The Graffiti Art stickers are sometimes, but not always, included with the basic set.

Box: 36 packs of 10 cards + 1 sticker. Common sets: approx. 2.40 per box if collation were perfect. Sticker sets: approximately 1.80 per box.
